nt-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDOvHyhEXVGh8Mf2JXnRId6MVuSzxnKmuagIbZnE9quRw&oe=67810FDB"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "CoverArtLandscape.png", "id": "415241234639995", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57572946_415241237973328_8860369148991174470_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=pVn0-gqEJn4Q7kNvgF7sTFF&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDoTuBGkMAn4TonY5Qv1T4AIv0jI6cOHpwFo9mT9FS6iQ&oe=678115B9"}, "display_name": "ROBMEMBOR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "\ud83e\udd16\ud83e\udd16\ud83e\udd16\nNavigate the labyrinthine corridors of an elderly woman's mind, whose memories have been broken by Alzheimer's. As the chosen mind-repairer, you will solve puzzles, guided by a witty robot, to piece together the tapestry of her life. Merge technology with empathy to revive beautiful memories from oblivion.\n\n\ud83e\udde9 Puzzle-Solving \ud83e\udde9\nExplore various environments, each packed with unique challenges to solve. As you successfully untangle these puzzles, you'll gather precious memories that belong to an elderly woman. Engage your inner Sherlock Holmes, crack the puzzles, and share in the joy of rebuilding lost memories!\n\n\u26a1\ufe0fUnleash the Potential of Brand New Powers! \u2728\nLevel up your puzzle-solving game: unleash unique powers to ghost your hands, clone objects and steal colors! \n\n\ud83d\udd27 Post-Launch Support \ud83d\udd27\nYour adventure doesn't end at launch! We've got your back with support for any hurdles you encounter or if you need some tips. Game on, confidently!\nYou can contact me at contact@palindromevr.com!!!\n", "short_description": "Help Hannah, an Alzheimer's patient,  by solving puzzles followed by a witty robot - become a mind repairer now!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://palindromevr.com/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Palindrome VR ", "support_